            <title>[KAFKA-9695] AdminClient allows null topic configs, but broker throws NPE</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-9695</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Config entries may contain null values, but broker&apos;s AdminManager throws NPE resulting in UnknownServerException. We should handle null values in configs.&lt;/p&gt;
